about.description: Fills missing values in a pandas DataFrame using a Restricted Boltzmann Machine.
about.summary: Fills missing values in a pandas DataFrame using a Restricted Boltzmann Machine.

name: boltzmannclean
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "boltzmannclean" %}
{% set version = "0.1.2" %}
{% set sha256 = "e4b4ed0a7ae9c1f3dfb9283c87fd1c846d801934f16afcf0e09ce5f24bc8d073" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - pandas
    - numpy
    - scipy
    - scikit-learn <=0.19

test:
  imports:
    - boltzmannclean

about:
  home: https://github.com/facultyai/boltzmannclean
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_family: Apache
  license_file: 'LICENSE'
  summary: 'Fills missing values in a pandas DataFrame using a Restricted Boltzmann Machine.'
  description: |
    Fills missing values in a pandas DataFrame using a Restricted Boltzmann Machine.

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - shwinnn
    - zblz
    - pbugnion
